{"id":314460,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-监察部门前警察施暴，多名访民被打伤（/","date":"2013-09-20T17:20:53Z","modified":"2013-09-20T17:20:53Z","title":"维权网 | 监察部门前警察施暴，多名访民被打伤（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员柴民报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日上午，来自吉林、辽宁、江苏等省市近六十名访民来到监察部门前喊冤，和往常一样访民遭到警察的驱赶，部分访民对警察的野蛮执法进行拍照，警察见状就掐住几位拍照访民的脖子，并把访民撂倒在地、抢访民正用作拍照的手机，其中一位身材矮小的女访民拼命挣扎，一位人伦丧尽的恶警竟然踩住了这位女访民的头。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>警察的暴行激起所有访民的愤慨，大家纷纷拿出笔来记这几个警察的警号，令人意想不到的一幕是，施暴的警察纷纷扯下警号并更加肆无忌惮地暴打被他们撂倒在地的访民，现场有数位访民被打伤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>被打伤的访民有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>人被抓走，目前下落不明。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-KMqHhEm5r90/UjxBrQxRyHI/AAAAAAAAobQ/4cdL0A00DQw/s1600/IMG_5213.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-KMqHhEm5r90/UjxBrQxRyHI/AAAAAAAAobQ/4cdL0A00DQw/s320/IMG_5213.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>现场亲历者李宗发</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,2